 >.  </p><p>Crafting with humans!  Bring your supplies and craft with us.  A
 ll ages welcome\, free event\, no purchase required.  All craft are welcome
 \, just avoid anything with fumes or loud noises.  Coloring books available
  if your craft is on a time out. Bring your own snacks &amp\; drinks or ord
 er delivery if you're hungry.  Indoor and outdoor seating available\, weath
 er permitting. </p><p><a href="https://rebelpurl.com/pages/craft-night-wedn
 esday-evenings">https://rebelpurl.com/pages/craft-night-wednesday-evenings<
 /a><br></p>
