UID:53ksl86p55ivoau56hn7f77fr7@google.com
CREATED:20241025T123908Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Learn the basics of knitting!</p><p>I knit continental\, so 
 that is what I teach.  That means I hold the yarn in my left hand and "pick
 " the yarn rather than holding yarn in my right hand and "throwing".  I can
  demonstrate "throwing" the yarn English style\, but when I am knitting\, i
 t will be continental.</p><p><strong>Masks are required for in-person meeti
 ngs.</strong></p><p><b>In this class\, we will go over the basics of the kn
 it and purl stitches.</b></p><p>Class will take place <strong>Saturday Janu
 ary 25th @11AM. </strong></p><p>Class will involve you learning and then tr
 ying out knit and purl stitches on different samples.  Samples will be wors
 ted and larger yarn with medium to larger needles. If you would like materi
 als to start your own project or would like to take a project worked on dur
 ing class home\, those will be available for purchase.  If your minds are r
 eady for more\, we can also go over long tail cast on and a typical bind of
 f.</p><p>Class will be open about 1-2 hours for playing\, but feel free to 
 hang in the shop after if you would like more help or yarn play time.</p><p
 ><a href="https://rebelpurl.com/products/basics-of-knitting-knit-and-purl?_
 pos=1&amp\;_psq=knit+basic&amp\;_ss=e&amp\;_v=1.0">https://rebelpurl.com/pr
 oducts/basics-of-knitting-knit-and-purl?_pos=1&amp\;_psq=knit+basic&amp\;_s
 s=e&amp\;_v=1.0</a><br></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T181347Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Knit & Purl Class
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
